headline.main: BRITISH SEA BATTLE MASKED IN SILENCE; London Awaits News of Clash With German Cruiser

lead_paragraph: LONDON, Jan. 1 -- London waited eagerly tonight for news of how a naval battle was going in the North Sea, where British units were reported last night to be in combat. It was not forthcoming.
abstract: London awaits news of naval clash off Norwegian coast
